---
export const prerender = false;
---

<section class="agent-showcase">
  <nav class="showcase-nav">
    <strong>Shortlist Platform</strong>
    <div>
      <a href="#features">Features</a>
      <a href="#buyer">Buyer Experience</a>
      <a href="#agent">Agent Tools</a>
      <a href="#demo" class="nav-cta">Book a demo</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">Built for modern real estate agents</p>
      <h1>A better way to send listings, read buyer intent, and win the follow-up.</h1>
      <p>
        Give buyers a polished private shortlist experience while you capture what they love,
        what they pass on, and what they want to see next.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#demo">Show me how it works</a>
        <a href="#features" class="secondary">Explore features</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-card">
      <div class="mock-browser">
        <div class="dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
        <div class="mock-image"></div>
        <div class="mock-body">
          <p class="mock-price">$849,900</p>
          <p>Curated shortlist for Sarah & Mike</p>
          <div class="reaction-row">
            <span>❤️ Love</span>
            <span>🤔 Maybe</span>
            <span>✕ Pass</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="stats-strip">
    <div><strong>Private</strong><span>buyer pages</span></div>
    <div><strong>Emotional</strong><span>listing feedback</span></div>
    <div><strong>Smart</strong><span>next-best matches</span></div>
    <div><strong>Agent</strong><span>CRM insights</span></div>
  </section>

  <section class="feature-intro" id="features">
    <p class="eyebrow">The full system</p>
    <h2>Everything an agent needs after “I’ll send you some listings.”</h2>
  </section>

  <section class="feature-grid">
    <article>
      <span>01</span>
      <h3>Private buyer shortlist pages</h3>
      <p>Send a clean branded page instead of a messy link dump. Buyers review homes in a focused, mobile-friendly experience.</p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <span>02</span>
      <h3>Love / maybe / pass feedback</h3>
      <p>Capture how buyers actually feel about each property instead of waiting for vague replies days later.</p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <span>03</span>
      <h3>Secondary “what stood out?” chips</h3>
      <p>Buyers can quickly tag what they liked - views, yard, kitchen, garage, layout, location, income potential, and more.</p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <span>04</span>
      <h3>Next higher-priced homes</h3>
      <p>When buyers finish a list, the system can suggest the next logical batch so the conversation keeps moving.</p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <span>05</span>
      <h3>Agent insight dashboard</h3>
      <p>See loved homes, maybes, passes, notes, tags, engagement, and buyer intent in one place.</p>
    </article>

    <article>
      <span>06</span>
      <h3>Text-message friendly</h3>
      <p>Send polished shortlist links by SMS and make the follow-up feel personal, fast, and professional.</p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="split-section dark" id="buyer">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Buyer experience</p>
      <h2>Feels more like browsing a product than opening a property feed.</h2>
      <p>
        Buyers get a smooth listing review flow with large photos, map context,
        clear property details, reactions, and simple next steps.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="phone-stack">
      <div class="phone-card">❤️ Loved<br><small>Updated kitchen, yard, location</small></div>
      <div class="phone-card">🤔 Maybe<br><small>Worth a second look</small></div>
      <div class="phone-card">✕ Not for me<br><small>Too small, wrong layout</small></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="split-section" id="agent">
    <div class="panel-preview">
      <div class="panel-line"></div>
      <div class="panel-line short"></div>
      <div class="mini-cards">
        <span>Buyer loved 3 homes</span>
        <span>Strong garage signal</span>
        <span>Ready for showings</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Agent tools</p>
      <h2>Turn buyer behaviour into better follow-up.</h2>
      <p>
        Instead of guessing, you can see which homes created interest, what features mattered,
        and what to send next.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="specs">
    <h2>Built for real agent workflows</h2>

    <div class="spec-grid">
      <div><strong>Shortlists</strong><span>Curated listing sets</span></div>
      <div><strong>CRM</strong><span>Buyer activity summaries</span></div>
      <div><strong>Maps</strong><span>Location-aware browsing</span></div>
      <div><strong>SMS</strong><span>Easy mobile sharing</span></div>
      <div><strong>Analytics</strong><span>Intent and engagement</span></div>
      <div><strong>Branding</strong><span>Agent-focused presentation</span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="final-cta" id="demo">
    <p class="eyebrow">For agents who want better conversations</p>
    <h2>Send better listing pages. Learn what buyers want. Follow up faster.</h2>
    <a href="mailto:chris@crump.ca">Book a demo</a>
  </section>
</section>

<style>
  :global(body) {
    margin: 0;
    background: #f4f0e8;
    color: #171411;
    font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
  }

  .agent-showcase {
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .showcase-nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 20;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 18px 32px;
    background: rgba(244, 240, 232, 0.86);
    backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .showcase-nav div {
    display: flex;
    gap: 22px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .showcase-nav a {
    color: #171411;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .nav-cta {
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #171411;
    color: #fff !important;
  }

  .hero {
    min-height: 92vh;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 80px 7vw;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #6b7f32;
  }

  h1, h2, h3, p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3.4rem, 7vw, 6.7rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.07em;
    max-width: 880px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.45rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .hero-copy p:not(.eyebrow),
  .split-section p,
  .feature-intro p:not(.eyebrow) {
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #5d574f;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 34px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hero-actions a,
  .final-cta a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 52px;
    padding: 0 22px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #171411;
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .hero-actions .secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: #171411;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
  }

  .hero-card {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .mock-browser {
    width: min(520px, 100%);
    border-radius: 34px;
    background: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 36px 100px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .dots {
    display: flex;
    gap: 7px;
    padding: 18px;
  }

  .dots span {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    background: #d9d3c8;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .mock-image {
    height: 330px;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(23,20,17,0.1), rgba(23,20,17,0.45)),
      url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585154340-be6161a56a0c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80");
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }

  .mock-body {
    padding: 26px;
  }

  .mock-price {
    font-size: 2.1rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    color: #171411 !important;
    margin: 0 0 6px !important;
  }

  .reaction-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .reaction-row span {
    padding: 12px 10px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: #f4f0e8;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .stats-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .stats-strip div {
    padding: 34px;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .stats-strip strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .stats-strip span {
    color: #6f675f;
  }

  .feature-intro {
    padding: 110px 7vw 30px;
  }

  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 18px;
    padding: 30px 7vw 120px;
  }

  .feature-grid article {
    min-height: 270px;
    padding: 28px;
    border-radius: 28px;
    background: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .feature-grid span {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    color: #8b8378;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .feature-grid p {
    margin-top: 14px;
    color: #5d574f;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .split-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 70px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 130px 7vw;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .split-section.dark {
    background: #171411;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .split-section.dark p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.68);
  }

  .phone-stack {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .phone-card {
    padding: 28px;
    border-radius: 28px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 950;
  }

  .phone-card small {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.62);
  }

  .panel-preview {
    padding: 34px;
    border-radius: 34px;
    background: #f4f0e8;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .panel-line {
    height: 42px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #171411;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .panel-line.short {
    width: 62%;
    opacity: 0.28;
  }

  .mini-cards {
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .mini-cards span {
    padding: 18px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    background: #fff;
    font-weight: 850;
  }

  .specs {
    padding: 120px 7vw;
  }

  .specs h2 {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin-bottom: 38px;
  }

  .spec-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .spec-grid div {
    padding: 34px;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .spec-grid strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .spec-grid span {
    color: #6f675f;
  }

  .final-cta {
    min-height: 70vh;
    padding: 120px 7vw;
    display: grid;
    place-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    background: #171411;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .final-cta h2 {
    max-width: 920px;
  }

  .final-cta a {
    margin: 34px auto 0;
    background: #fff;
    color: #171411;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .showcase-nav div {
      display: none;
    }

    .hero,
    .split-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 70px 24px;
    }

    .stats-strip,
    .feature-grid,
    .spec-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .feature-intro,
    .feature-grid,
    .specs,
    .final-cta {
      padding-left: 24px;
      padding-right: 24px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 3.6rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    .mock-image {
      height: 250px;
    }
  }
</style>